          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>We the People Commission on Full Representation Act of 2019 </b></p> <p>This bill establishes the We the People Commission on Full Representation. The commission must develop proposals and report to Congress regarding voting representation for </p> <ul> <li>Puerto Rico, </li> <li>the District of Columbia, </li> <li>Guam, </li> <li>the U.S. Virgin Islands, </li> <li>American Samoa, and </li> <li>the Northern Mariana Islands. </li> </ul>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-03-28T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
